You go not till I set you up a glass
Where you may see the inmost part of you.
[Gertrude] What wilt thou do? Thou wilt not murder me?
Help, help, ho!
[Polonius] What ho! Help, help, help!
[Hamlet] How now, a rat? Dead for a ducat, dead!
